{"tid":2511415,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【離鄉以後你還好嗎？】台灣流亡抗爭者以攝影療傷：誰想一世被稱流亡手足？","createTime":"2021-05-01T01:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T13:51:53.000Z","uid":126919,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"81b8f0d4090e834f6d2241f1602d402921b51756","tid":2511415,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T01:50:11.000Z","msg":"Kenneth（化名）與不少流亡抗爭者一樣，要依賴藥物方能入眠。拍攝就成為他療傷的方式。拍攝時，他只需專心留意街上的趣事，並用鏡頭紀錄，得到一刻的放鬆。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「說實話有誰會想不斷宣稱自己是流亡手足一輩子，我們都希望可以自立。我不知道未來的自己會如何，會否有機會有台灣的居留身份，但其實我覺得只要有為香港付出的心仍然存在，你一天都是香港人。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳細報道 ➡️ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3e3BiMj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3e3BiMj&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRK6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=59c86675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3e3BiMj</a>"},{"pid":"25bed613f54d21b299c874db828f28eed10c09bd","tid":2511415,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T02:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905a5a23342c9cbdb6b9dde81e3efaa651b7407b","tid":2511415,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25bed613f54d21b299c874db828f28eed10c09bd","tid":2511415,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T02:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"h